    "索引只列出目前有有效紀錄的項目。",
    "排序依紀錄筆數由多到少。",
    "點世界名稱（若有連結）可直接前往該賽道世界。"
  ],
  "sidebar_en": [
    "The index only lists entries that currently have valid runs.",
    "Ordering is by run count, most runs first.",
    "World names link out to their source world when a URL is available."
  ],
